{"parentUuid":"e5f0be85-8d7b-4d30-85ba-9e71ec3c2b66","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01DYgKN9SmXSgdbXf94wtARZ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1480,"cache_read_input_tokens":10922,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1480},"output_tokens":0,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"}},"requestId":"req_011CZJogLogQLC2rBC57Mr8d","type":"assistant","uuid":"4ae175b0-e7ca-4d1d-9fec-e41d247339a0","timestamp":"2026-03-22T21:11:05.175Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"a0d84377-931f-4f90-a408-e626f9936836","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"main"}
{"parentUuid":"4ae175b0-e7ca-4d1d-9fec-e41d247339a0","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01DYgKN9SmXSgdbXf94wtARZ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## golang-migrate のトランザクション管理\n\nはい、デフォルトで**1ファイル = 1トランザクション**として実行されます。\n\n```\nBEGIN;\n  CREATE FUNCTION ...\n  CREATE EXTENSION ...\n  CREATE TABLE \"categories\" ...\n  ...\nCOMMIT;  ← 全成功時のみ\n```\n\n途中でエラーが発生すると `ROLLBACK` されるため、「途中まで適用された」状態にはなりません。\n\n---\n\n### ただし例外がある\n\n一部の DDL はトランザクション内で実行できません：\n\n```sql\nCREATE INDEX CONCURRENTLY ...   -- NG（今回は通常INDEXなのでOK）\nCREATE DATABASE ...             -- NG\nDROP DATABASE ...               -- NG\nVACUUM ...                      -- NG\n```\n\n今回のファイルには該当するものはないので問題なし。\n\n---\n\n### 今回のセミコロン欠落との関係\n\n57行目のセミコロン欠落はトランザクション云々より先に**SQL パース時点でエラー**になり、マイグレーション全体が実行されずにロールバックされます。結果として安全側に倒れますが、修正は必要です。\n\n---\n\n### トランザクションを無効にしたい場合\n\n`CREATE INDEX CONCURRENTLY` などを使う場合は、ファイル先頭にコメントを追記します：\n\n```sql\n-- migrate:no-transaction  (golang-migrate の場合)\n```"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1480,"cache_read_input_tokens":10922,"output_tokens":1065,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1480,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZJogLogQLC2rBC57Mr8d","type":"assistant","uuid":"d15d927d-5ebe-4cde-a99e-80fd81ce16c2","timestamp":"2026-03-22T21:11:12.784Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"a0d84377-931f-4f90-a408-e626f9936836","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"main"}
